ter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/81307/', '', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole', 'Vincristine, Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Paclitaxel, Topotecan, Teniposide, Irinotecan, Vinorelbine, Etoposide, Docetaxel', 1767369485);
